<subSubSection id="CAFB653AFFFAF12BFF210DC2D7BAAB46" pageId="14" pageNumber="239" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="825E36B1FFFAF12BFF210DC2D7BAAB46" blockId="14.[130,776,1682,1900]" pageId="14" pageNumber="239">
The specimens collected by Morales Agacino and his colleagues are a valuable source of data to document the distribution of several species. We give here two examples, i.e., 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFAF12BFD230C02D72CAB66" authority="Morales Agacino, 1945" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1945" class="Insecta" family="Pamphagidae" genus="Glauvarovia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mendizabali">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFAF12BFD230C02D425AB61" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="239">Glauvarovia mendizabali</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFAF12BFEAB0C21D72CAB66" author="Morales Agacino" box="[270,524,1841,1868]" firstAuthor="Morales Agacino" journalOrPublisher="Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia" pageId="14" pageNumber="239" pagination="310 - 339" part="20" publicationUrl="http://hdl.handle.net/10261/148685" refId="ref12923" refString="MORALES AGACINO E. 1945 a. - Algunos datos sobre orthopteroides del Sahara Occidental. Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia 20 (3 - 4): 310 - 339. http: // hdl. handle. net / 10261 / 148685" title="Algunos datos sobre orthopteroides del Sahara Occidental" type="journal article" year="1945">Morales Agacino, 1945</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFAF12BFDE30C22D408AB46" authority="(Bolivar, 1936)" baseAuthorityName="Bolivar" baseAuthorityYear="1936" class="Insecta" family="Pamphagidae" genus="Paracinipe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exarata">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFAF12BFDE30C22D626AB61" box="[582,774,1842,1867]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="239">Paracinipe exarata</emphasis>
(Bolivar, 1936)
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFAF12BFE930C41D7ADAB46" authority="Burmeister, 1840" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1840" box="[310,653,1873,1900]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphagidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Pamphagidae Burmeister, 1840</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
